278
00:33:28.206 --> 00:33:30.265
<i>And they begln to mate.</i>

279
00:33:31.609 --> 00:33:35.807
<i>The female's response is surprising.</i>

280
00:33:36.447 --> 00:33:40.281
<i>The male becomes her prey.</i>

281
00:33:40.351 --> 00:33:47.587
<i>She slowly eats off his head</i>
<i>while they are matlng.</i>

282
00:33:49.027 --> 00:33:50.153
<i>Eventually...</i>

283
00:33:50.228 --> 00:33:52.628
<i>the male succumbs to death.</i>

284
00:34:01.272 --> 00:34:05.868
