Are you drunk?

297
00:36:27.985 --> 00:36:29.782
Those photos...

298
00:36:29.854 --> 00:36:31.446
Where did you hide them?

299
00:36:31.522 --> 00:36:32.819
Give them to me.

300
00:36:34.592 --> 00:36:36.184
Remember that bitch.

301
00:36:36.427 --> 00:36:37.758
Calm down.

302
00:36:37.895 --> 00:36:39.692
What photos
are you talking about?

303
00:36:39.764 --> 00:36:41.129
J ust give them to me!

304
00:36:41.199 --> 00:36:43.895
Please calm down.

305
00:36:44.202 --> 00:36:46.193
Tonn. calm down.

306
00:36:46.270 --> 00:36:48.101
What photos?

307
00:36:52.977 --> 00:36:54.205
Tonn.

308
00:36:54.278 --> 00:36:56.803
I'll call your wife.

309
00:37:38.556 --> 00:37:40.114
