310
00:37:41.692 --> 00:37:43.387
Cleaning up.

311
00:37:49.367 --> 00:37:51.028
Your neck still sore?

312
00:37:52.703 --> 00:37:53.670
Yeah.

313
00:37:53.738 --> 00:37:56.935
Take it easy. Don't work so much.

314
00:42:26.277 --> 00:42:28.711
NATRE NAPA CHAN-NGAM.
HONOR SOCIETY 1995

315
00:42:40.491 --> 00:42:41.890
<i>Tonn.</i>

316
00:42:42.192 --> 00:42:43.853
<i>It's me. Tun.</i>

317
00:42:45.362 --> 00:42:47.455
Are you home?

318
00:43:01.178 --> 00:43:02.611
Tonn.

319
00:43:04.415 --> 00:43:06.849
Are you home?

320
00:43:15.025 --> 00:43:16.652
Tonn.

321
00:43:40.718 --> 00:43:42.709
NATRE NAPA CHAN-NGAM

322
00:44:28.999 --> 00:44:32.457
Tonn! Tonn!

323
00:44:42.546 --> 00:44:44.377
Tonn!

324
00:45:20.618 --> 00:45:22.449
I'm really sorry.

325
00:45:23.221 --> 00:45:26.987
Do you know
what was bothering him?

326
00:45:30.161 --> 00:45:31.924
No. Suddenly he...

327
00:45:31.996 --> 00:45:35.227
It's your gang's fault.

328
00:45:36.534 --> 00:45:38.434
Have you all gone insane?

329
00:45:39.770 --> 00:45:41.670
What do you mean?

330
00:45:42.206 --> 00:45:45.334
You've all committed suicide.

331
00:45:45.576 --> 00:45:47.100
Who?

332
00:45:48.212 --> 00:45:49.839
Don't you know?

333
00:45:50.281 --> 00:45:54.012
Your other two friends
also killed themselves.

334
00:45:54.619 --> 00:45:56.314
Which two?

335
00:45:59.190 --> 00:46:03.024
The two who sat next to you
on my wedding day.

336
00:46:47.471 --> 00:46:49.132
<i>Who's this woman?</i>

337
00:46:53.177 --> 00:46:55.008
Where did you get that?

338
00:46:55.880 --> 00:46:58.747
She's the shadow in the photos. right?

339
00:46:59.517 --> 00:47:01.417
Who is she?

340
00:47:03.921 --> 00:47:06.412
How did you know her?

341
00:47:24.141 --> 00:47:27.235
<i>I knew her in college.</i>

342
00:47:29.046 --> 00:47:31.014
<i>Her name is Natre.</i>

343
00:47:34.118 --> 00:47:37.986
<i>She was a quiet person...</i>

344
00:47:38.356 --> 00:47:40.449
<i>without any friends.</i>

345
00:47:43.160 --> 00:47:46.721
<i>We all thought she was weird.</i>

346
00:47:50.134 --> 00:47:52.261
<i>I felt sorry for her.</i>

347
00:47:59.410 --> 00:48:03.346
<i>We dated but I kept it secret.</i>

348
00:48:05.082 --> 00:48:07.346
<i>She loved me very much.</i>

349
00:50:57.655 --> 00:51:00.249
She threatened to slit her wrists.

350
00:51:01.425 --> 00:51:03.359
I didn't know what to do.

351
00:51:03.427 --> 00:51:05.588
My friends thought it was funny.

352
00:51:05.663 --> 00:51:07.255
<i>How were they involved?</i>

353
00:51:07.331 --> 00:51:09.265
<i>Why are they dead?</i>

354
00:51:09.333 --> 00:51:10.493
They...

355
00:51:10.568 --> 00:51:12.365
What did they do?

356
00:51:14.538 --> 00:51:16.199
I don't know.

357
00:51:17.274 --> 00:51:20.505
Tonn said he'd take care of it.

358
00:51:23.013 --> 00:51:25.880
After that. Natre disappeared.

359
00:51:26.917 --> 00:51:29.010
I never saw her again.

360
00:51:29.720 --> 00:51:32.917
Didn't you try to stop them?

361
00:51:33.824 --> 00:51:36.987
<i>How could you let it happen?</i>

362
00:51:43.234 --> 00:51:45.361
What could I do?

363
00:51:47.137 --> 00:51:49.697
Now everyone is dead.

364
00:51:52.810 --> 00:51:54.107
<i>I'm...</i>

365
00:51:54.478 --> 00:51:57.242
I'm going to die next.

366
00:52:34.685 --> 00:52:36.175
It's funny...

367
00:52:38.255 --> 00:52:44.216
how we always say
if we could turn back time...

368
00:52:45.596 --> 00:52:48.531
we would reverse all our wrongs.

369
00:52:51.368 --> 00:52:53.666
<i>Do you thlnk she's okay?</i>

370
00:52:54.138 --> 00:52:56.402
<i>Will we find her there tomorrow?</i>

371
00:52:56.473 --> 00:52:57.997
Go to sleep.

372
00:52:59.877 --> 00:53:02.710
I'll keep you company tonight.

373
00:55:06.136 --> 00:55:07.967
Excuse me.

374
00:55:08.338 --> 00:55:10.704
Do you have any toilet paper?

375
00:55:44.875 --> 00:55:46.672
Can I poo first?

376
00:55:46.744 --> 00:55:48.177
I'm sorry.

377
00:56:56.947 --> 00:56:58.676
What's bothering you?

378
00:57:12.329 --> 00:57:14.320
What's wrong?

379
00:57:25.809 --> 00:57:27.333
What is it?

380
00:58:18.729 --> 00:58:20.629
Is it around here?

381
00:58:31.441 --> 00:58:32.635
Excuse me.

382
00:58:32.709 --> 00:58:34.438
Do you know where this is?

383
00:58:38.548 --> 00:58:40.982
Mom. where is this house?

384
00:59:14.418 --> 00:59:15.817
Ma'am.

385
00:59:28.332 --> 00:59:29.492
Excuse me.

386
00:59:29.566 --> 00:59:31.830
<i>Is this Natre's house?</i>

387
00:59:32.903 --> 00:59:34.495
What do you want?

388
00:59:35.472 --> 00:59:36.837
Well...

389
00:59:36.907 --> 00:59:39.307
we're her friends.

390
00:59:39.509 --> 00:59:43.001
Natre's friends? Come inside.

391
00:59:53.090 --> 00:59:55.684
Have some water. You must be tired.

392
00:59:55.759 --> 00:59:57.727
Did you drive from Bangkok?

393
00:59:58.495 --> 00:59:59.427
Yes.

394
01:00:04.267 --> 01:00:06.792
We'd like to ask about Natre.

395
01:00:07.304 --> 01:00:09.636
She's not feeling well.

396
01:00:09.706 --> 01:00:11.833
<i>She's taking a nap.</i>

397
01:00:12.709 --> 01:00:14.506
Should I wake her?

398
01:00:18.515 --> 01:00:20.483
Stay for dinner.

399
01:00:20.817 --> 01:00:22.284
I was about to cook.

400
01:00:22.352 --> 01:00:25.480
I'm making her favorite dish.

401
01:00:26.323 --> 01:00:28.291
Natre will be so happy.

402
01:00:28.358 --> 01:00:30.724
Her friends don't visit often.

403
01:00:30.794 --> 01:00:32.659
<i>Wait right here.</i>

404
01:00:51.448 --> 01:00:53.177
Where are you going?

405
01:02:07.290 --> 01:02:08.655
<i>How dare you!</i>

406
01:02:14.664 --> 01:02:16.894
<i>Did she commit suicide?</i>

407
01:02:21.538 --> 01:02:23.904
We should cremate her.

408
01:02:25.809 --> 01:02:26.798
No.

409
01:02:26.877 --> 01:02:29.607
I won't cremate her.

410
01:02:30.347 --> 01:02:31.905
Ma'am...

411
01:02:32.983 --> 01:02:36.419
I don't know if you believe
such things...

412
01:02:36.486 --> 01:02:40.388
but I'd like you to look
at these photos.

413
01:02:40.457 --> 01:02:45.053
They were taken around campus.

414
01:02:47.297 --> 01:02:49.424
Some of the places...

415
01:02:49.499 --> 01:02:52.900
were rooms Natre had been in.

416
01:02:54.571 --> 01:02:57.233
And these shadows appeared.

417
01:03:00.877 --> 01:03:02.970
I think that...

418
01:03:03.046 --> 01:03:06.482
Natre's spirit is restless.

419
01:03:07.484 --> 01:03:09.782
Natre...

420
01:03:12.389 --> 01:03:14.983
My dear Natre.

421
01:03:16.193 --> 01:03:20.095
Why don't you visit me?

422
01:03:26.636 --> 01:03:29.730
Can you tell me what happened?

423
01:03:29.806 --> 01:03:31.865
Why did she leave Bangkok?

424
01:03:40.217 --> 01:03:42.082
Ma'am...

425
01:03:43.520 --> 01:03:44.782
Ma'am.

426
01:03:46.089 --> 01:03:48.148
<i>These shadows...</i>

427
01:03:48.225 --> 01:03:53.094
<i>might mean her spirit is not at peace.</i>

428
01:03:56.099 --> 01:03:59.626
We should hold her funeral.

429
01:03:59.703 --> 01:04:02.228
Please.

430
01:04:15.218 --> 01:04:18.449
<i>When she came home.</i>
<i>she seemed different.</i>

431
01:04:18.521 --> 01:04:20.580
<i>She wouldn't talk to anyone.</i>

432
01:04:20.657 --> 01:04:23.751
<i>No one knows what happened</i>
<i>in Bangkok.</i>

433
01:04:24.261 --> 01:04:27.526
<i>Then she overdosed on pills.</i>

434
01:04:27.597 --> 01:04:32.694
<i>Luckily. her mother found her</i>
<i>and got her to the hospital on time.</i>

435
01:04:32.769 --> 01:04:36.170
When she recovered...

436
01:04:36.239 --> 01:04:43.543
she climbed on the hospital roof
and jumped off the edge.

437
01:04:43.613 --> 01:04:47.344
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

438
01:04:48.485 --> 01:04:52.387
She's been distraught
ever since Natre's death.

439
01:04:52.455 --> 01:04:56.915
No matter what.
she refused to cremate her.

440
01:04:56.993 --> 01:04:59.894
<i>All the villagers were scared.</i>

441
01:04:59.963 --> 01:05:03.160
<i>No one wanted to talk to her.</i>

442
01:07:05.555 --> 01:07:07.921
Can't sleep?

443
01:07:12.595 --> 01:07:15.325
Tell me the truth...

444
01:07:15.398 --> 01:07:18.162
did you love Natre?

445
01:07:21.337 --> 01:07:23.771
I tried to...

446
01:07:29.112 --> 01:07:32.206
I believed that one day I would.

447
01:07:37.287 --> 01:07:40.586
But I was fooling myself.

448
01:07:47.230 --> 01:07:53.465
When I broke it off.
I was a total asshole.

449
01:07:58.541 --> 01:08:01.840
But she still loved me the same.

450
01:08:06.816 --> 01:08:10.343
I want this to be over.

451
01:08:10.787 --> 01:08:13.221
If she wants me to die. I will.

452
01:08:14.123 --> 01:08:16.785
Don't say that.

453
01:08:16.860 --> 01:08:19.727
It's almost over.

454
01:08:19.796 --> 01:08:22.731
No. it's not.

455
01:08:26.336 --> 01:08:28.964
I know she'll come for me.

456
01:08:29.038 --> 01:08:31.165
Tun.

457
01:08:31.241 --> 01:08:35.200
We've come this far.

458
01:08:35.278 --> 01:08:38.145
And you're sorry for what you did.

459
01:08:38.214 --> 01:08:41.615
I'm sure she knows.

460
01:08:42.051 --> 01:08:45.043
Don't talk about death anymore.

461
01:08:51.127 --> 01:08:53.391
I'm sorry.

462
01:08:58.167 --> 01:09:00.260
Do you still love me?

463
01:09:05.408 --> 01:09:08.275
No matter what.
you won't leave me. right?

464
01:10:47.877 --> 01:10:50.744
Jane.

465
01:12:23.005 --> 01:12:24.131
Tun...

466
01:12:24.207 --> 01:12:25.936
Jane...

467
01:12:26.008 --> 01:12:28.772
Where did you go?

468
01:12:28.845 --> 01:12:31.075
Why did you leave me alone?

469
01:12:31.147 --> 01:12:32.910
We've got to leave.

470
01:12:35.985 --> 01:12:38.453
Asshole!

471
01:12:38.521 --> 01:12:40.318
Why did you leave me?

472
01:12:40.389 --> 01:12:42.220
Didn't you love me?

473
01:12:42.291 --> 01:12:45.556
How could you leave me?

474
01:12:46.996 --> 01:12:49.362
How could you leave me?

475
01:14:28.297 --> 01:14:29.787
Tun...

476
01:14:29.866 --> 01:14:32.164
Are you feeling better?

477
01:14:33.936 --> 01:14:36.962
What happened last night?

478
01:14:37.039 --> 01:14:39.473
Tun...

479
01:14:39.542 --> 01:14:43.069
Jane...

480
01:14:49.285 --> 01:14:52.846
The abbot said
Natre will be cremated today.

481
01:14:56.225 --> 01:14:57.886
It's over.

482
01:16:53.576 --> 01:16:55.476
- Hello.
- Hello. Jane.

483
01:16:55.544 --> 01:16:57.341
Picking up photos?

484
01:16:57.413 --> 01:17:00.007
- Where's Tun?
- He's busy.

485
01:17:00.082 --> 01:17:01.413
Good.

486
01:17:01.484 --> 01:17:04.510
When he's busy.
I get to see you.

487
01:17:12.094 --> 01:17:14.289
You went on vacation?

488
01:17:14.363 --> 01:17:15.921
Yes. we went to the beach.

489
01:17:15.998 --> 01:17:17.761
When did you go?

490
01:17:17.833 --> 01:17:20.324
Last week.

491
01:17:22.071 --> 01:17:24.665
This photo is...

492
01:17:27.243 --> 01:17:28.801
What's wrong?

493
01:17:34.383 --> 01:17:35.873
Did you gain weight?

494
01:17:38.220 --> 01:17:40.950
I didn't recognize you.

495
01:17:42.158 --> 01:17:43.989
Hi.

496
01:17:44.060 --> 01:17:45.857
J umbo prints.

497
01:17:46.862 --> 01:17:49.194
Write your name. please.

498
01:20:27.523 --> 01:20:29.423
Get her. guys!

499
01:21:04.627 --> 01:21:05.992
Jane...

500
01:21:06.061 --> 01:21:09.121
Why are you crying?

501
01:21:10.866 --> 01:21:13.357
Asshole...

502
01:21:14.470 --> 01:21:16.700
How could you be so cruel?

503
01:21:22.211 --> 01:21:23.940
Where did you find these?

504
01:21:26.015 --> 01:21:31.317
If I didn't find them.
I'd be a fool forever. right?

505
01:21:35.791 --> 01:21:38.521
Let me explain.

506
01:21:40.562 --> 01:21:43.224
What's there to say?

507
01:21:46.635 --> 01:21:48.694
I always believe you.

508
01:21:55.177 --> 01:21:57.737
I thought I knew you.

509
01:22:11.293 --> 01:22:12.282
Tun.

510
01:22:13.329 --> 01:22:16.059
Take her picture
so she doesn't rat on us.

511
01:22:16.432 --> 01:22:18.332
Tun. help me.

512
01:22:19.868 --> 01:22:22.564
I know it was wrong.

513
01:22:22.604 --> 01:22:24.697
Take her picture now!

514
01:22:25.441 --> 01:22:27.238
<i>What's wrong!</i>

515
01:22:28.477 --> 01:22:30.104
I'm your buddy!

516
01:22:30.179 --> 01:22:32.272
Hurry!

517
01:22:40.222 --> 01:22:42.622
Tun. help me.

518
01:22:55.437 --> 01:22:57.234
I never forgave myself.

519
01:22:57.306 --> 01:22:59.831
But I was young and stupid.

520
01:23:00.309 --> 01:23:03.005
I've heard enough.

521
01:23:03.679 --> 01:23:06.773
I want to go home.

522
01:24:00.202 --> 01:24:02.227
Come on out!

523
01:24:06.175 --> 01:24:07.802
Where are you?

524
01:24:14.249 --> 01:24:16.410
I thought you loved me!

525
01:24:18.086 --> 01:24:19.849
Loved me so much!

526
01:24:27.329 --> 01:24:29.456
Till death do us part!

527
01:24:34.670 --> 01:24:37.138
She's gone now.

528
01:26:15.804 --> 01:26:19.433
Sometimes
spirits long for their loved ones.

